import React, { Component } from "react"

export class IconLayoutText extends Component<any, null> {
  render() {
    return (
      <svg
        className="layout-text"
        width="45px"
        height="30px"
        viewBox="0 0 45 30"
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      >
        <g stroke="none" strokeWidth="1" fill="none" fillRule="evenodd">
          <g
            className="layout-text-group"
            fill={this.props.fill ? this.props.fill : "#000"}
          >
            <polyline points="0 2 34 2 34 0 0 0" />
            <polyline points="0 7 26 7 26 5 0 5" />
            <rect x="0" y="10" width="45" height="20" />
          </g>
        </g>
      </svg>
    )
  }
}
